# ==========================================
# V.A.N.T.i.S. ARCHITECTURE
# ==========================================
# This repository is 100% PRIVATE.
# All vault/ directories and logs/ are tracked for cross-device sync.
# The public portfolio is managed via /gh:publish to a separate mirror repo.

# --- 1. TECHNICAL & OS GARBAGE ---
.DS_Store
.obsidian/workspace.json
.obsidian/plugins/terminal/data.json
.obsidian/appearance.json
**/__pycache__/
**/.venv/
**/.pytest_cache/
*.pyc

# --- 2. EMBEDDED REPOS & RESEARCH ASSETS ---
# Research clones that contain their own .git — must not be tracked as submodules
02_MACHINE/Research/everything-claude-code/

# --- 3. EPHEMERAL SESSION FILES ---
.gemini/tmp/
.obsidian/themes/

# --- 4. AGENT CONFIG EXCEPTIONS ---
# This is a 100% private repo. Agent config is part of the architecture and must be tracked.
# These override the global gitignore which excludes .claude/ by default.
!.claude/settings.local.json
!.claude/commands/
!.claude/commands/**

# --- 5. SECURITY & SECRETS ---
.env*
*.key
*.pem
credentials.json
secrets.yaml
# NEVER commit the token file if you use the GitHub MCP or gh CLI.
.gh_token*
